{"tid":2018882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"The Truth About Hong Kong文宣 \"是你教我們和平遊行是沒用\"","createTime":"2020-05-16T01:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T16:38:22.000Z","uid":12929,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7e73daf4f15635615e766d0aecc6801edf883206","tid":2018882,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:49:56.000Z","msg":"致香港人、手足:<br />\n<br />\n林奠個 <span style=\"color: violet;\">The Truth About Hong Kong</span> 真係個好好嘅平台俾國際睇到，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人作為民族，共對暴政下不屈嘅精神。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n國際要認清香港人團結、抗爭、不屈、創新嘅精神，係造就香港民族嘅必須品。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">文宣主軸以香港作為對抗暴政最前線</span>要面對以positivity 為主線，帶出香港人爭取主權在民、自由民主，堅持維護普世價值嘅毅力。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">宜</span></strong></span><br />\n1. 沒有停止的週末大遊行<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pK73QQY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpK73QQY.png&h=30a783b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. &quot;是你教我們和平遊行是沒用&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/65681428_T0wHf_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F65681428_T0wHf_1200x0.png&h=0a2e898d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">忌</span></strong></span><br />\n警暴畫面 (因為咁係示弱)。<br />\n1. 自己上網睇，有點兒多。"},{"pid":"4d521d7a96b7e6e8de167d227c5f0b2176d3ca32","tid":2018882,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"國際文宣做嘢啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757399e728873e0504eb36ba9446decdab52de85","tid":2018882,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T01:56:11.000